==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hazy
<hw>Ha"zy</hw> <pr>(h⟦amac⟧"z⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Haze</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Thick with haze;
somewhat obscured with haze; not clear or transparent.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A
tender, <xex>hazy</xex> brightness.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Wordsworth.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Obscure; confused; not clear; <as>as, a
<ex>hazy</ex> argument; a <ex>hazy</ex> intellect.</as></def>
<rj><au>Mrs. Gore.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>H-bomb</ent>⟦br⟧
